(8538, '|L290-With grace and beauty the cervid lope across the land. Their elegant lines a delight to behold. Joy to the viewer, prey to the predator. This is the cycle eternal, a beginning, and an end.|l', 8551, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8538
(8552, '|L296-A Meditation on |l|L290-Separation|l|n|n', 8540, 0, 1, 42423), -- 8552
(8389, '|L294-Creation|l|L295-, growth, |l|L290-life.|l|L295- Everything |l|L294-bursts|l|L295- forth from the spark of idea. |l|L290-Death|l|L294- is an ending|l|L295- that they rebuild from. Anything |l|L290-broken|l|L295- can be fixed with proper care and |l|L294-culling.|l', 0, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8389
(8535, '|L290-I |lhear |L290-their song ring out across the water. Melodies in the pattern telling stories to all. Jumping. Swimming. Running. Bulbous and majestic, they stand strong.|l', 8548, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8535
(8533, '|L294-The |l|L290-Circles|l|L294- are industrious. True beings of |l|L290-harmony.|l|L294- Their thoughts flow like a river that |l|L290-breaks|l|L294- into smaller and |l|L290-smaller|l|L294- channels that feed once again into the greater stream. There is no |l|L290-beginning|l|L294- or end to them, they are |l|L290-always|l|L294- whole.|l', 8546, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8533
(8534, '|L290-Secrets|l|L295- must be kept. Stored|l|L294- away.|l|L295- Contained safely so that they may be |l|L294-revealed at the |l|L295-correct time and place. |l|L290-A secret|l|L295- told too soon is |l|L294-ruinous|l|L295- to all. The |l|L290-archives|l|L295- maintain the balance. The grand design of the First Ones must be |l|L294-protected|l|L295- at all costs.|l', 8547, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8534
(8547, '|L290-Variations on Majesty|l|n|n', 8535, 0, 1, 42423), -- 8547
(8412, '|L295-Existence is |l|L290-contextual.|l|L295- The |l|L294-light |l|L295-cannot be defined without the |l|L290-dark|l|L295-, to have |l|L294-one requires|l|L295- the other. Language is also |l|L290-contextual|l|L295-, there is only meaning with reasoning. The |l|L294-deeper|l|L295- the reasoning, the ever |l|L290-changing|l|L295- the meaning. Their thoughts encompass everything and |l|L290-nothing|l|L295- all at once. They are what|l|L294- we cannot|l|L295- comprehend.|l', 8544, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8412
