(8380, '|L290-With grace and|l beauty |L290-the cervid lope across the|l land|L290-. Their elegant lines a delight to behold.|l Joy |L290-to the viewer, prey to the predator. This is the cycle eternal, a beginning, and an|l end.', 0, 0, 0, 42423), -- 8380
